00:11:23,625 --> 00:11:25,085
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay. Fine.</font>

206
00:11:31,025 --> 00:11:32,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Move.</font>

207
00:11:40,155 --> 00:11:43,555
<font color=#FFFF00>It was dangerous. It is because of my foolish husband.</font>

208
00:11:51,755 --> 00:11:52,985
<font color=#FFFF00>Mr. Kim,</font>

209
00:11:53,555 --> 00:11:56,725
<font color=#FFFF00>please count me out this.</font>

210
00:11:56,885 --> 00:11:59,425
<font color=#FFFF00>I gave you the advice personally...</font>

211
00:11:59,585 --> 00:12:02,685
<font color=#FFFF00>without expecting anything in return.</font>

212
00:12:03,085 --> 00:12:06,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Why do newspapers say it was an advice on tax evasion?</font>

213
00:12:06,655 --> 00:12:08,155
<font color=#FFFF00>How pathetic.</font>

214
00:12:09,185 --> 00:12:10,425
<font color=#FFFF00>I know...</font>

215
00:12:10,755 --> 00:12:14,155
<font color=#FFFF00>the collusion between Minjeong Party and Seonghan has been revealed,</font>

216
00:12:14,285 --> 00:12:17,285
<font color=#FFFF00>but I have no idea why I am involved in that.</font>

217
00:12:17,485 --> 00:12:21,485
<font color=#FFFF00>I have been nominated because they found me competent.</font>

218
00:12:21,785 --> 00:12:25,125
<font color=#FFFF00>It has nothing to do with the advice.</font>

219
00:12:25,125 --> 00:12:26,585
<font color=#FFFF00>Am I wrong?</font>

220
00:12:26,585 --> 00:12:27,825
<font color=#FFFF00>How silly.</font>

221
00:12:29,125 --> 00:12:34,285
<font color=#FFFF00>I will stay in my office and avoid the reporters.</font>

222
00:12:34,955 --> 00:12:38,085
<font color=#FFFF00>Please handle this well and save me.</font>

223
00:12:39,555 --> 00:12:40,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay.</font>

224
00:12:41,985 --> 00:12:45,285
<font color=#FFFF00>I will not go outside for a week.</font>

225
00:12:46,685 --> 00:12:49,755
<font color=#FFFF00>I will. Please call me. Goodbye.</font>

226
00:12:55,125 --> 00:12:56,125
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Hoon,</font>

227
00:12:56,985 --> 00:12:59,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Senior Secretary Kim said he'll take care of this.</font>

228
00:13:00,055 --> 00:13:02,025
<font color=#FFFF00>He just wants me to stay in...</font>

229
00:13:02,225 --> 00:13:03,955
<font color=#FFFF00>and not see any reporters.</font>

230
00:13:04,925 --> 00:13:07,785
<font color=#FFFF00>Staying inside won't settle anything.</font>

231
00:13:08,255 --> 00:13:11,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Senior Secretary Kim will resolve the situation.</font>

232
00:13:13,125 --> 00:13:15,825
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sure he's also in trouble like you.</font>

233
00:13:16,385 --> 00:13:17,725
<font color=#FFFF00>He is very...</font>

234
00:13:19,485 --> 00:13:22,755
<font color=#FFFF00>- Who... Who is it? - It's me.</font>

235
00:13:23,485 --> 00:13:24,785
<font color=#FFFF00>This is your wife.</font>

236
00:13:28,925 --> 00:13:30,055
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness.</font>

237
00:13:32,355 --> 00:13:34,825
<font color=#FFFF00>- Honey, I missed you. - Hello, Hee Sook.</font>

238
00:13:36,485 --> 00:13:38,555
<font color=#FFFF00>You're totally useless!</font>

239
00:13:39,725 --> 00:13:42,925
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you not to enter the political arena.</font>

240
00:13:43,855 --> 00:13:46,325
<font color=#FFFF00>- Honey. - What will you do now?</font>

241
00:13:46,425 --> 00:13:48,155
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell me what your plan is.</font>

242
00:13:48,255 --> 00:13:51,055
<font color=#FFFF00>If you lose your title as a lawyer because of this,</font>

243
00:13:51,125 --> 00:13:54,185
<font color=#FFFF00>how will we make a living? Tell me!</font>

244
00:13:54,325 --> 00:13:55,625
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop it!</font>

245
00:13:55,985 --> 00:13:57,785
<font color=#FFFF00>It will be all right!</font>

246
00:13:58,085 --> 00:14:00,585
<font color=#FFFF00>It will be settled soon!</font>

247
00:14:01,555 --> 00:14:05,385
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you to just work hard as a lawyer.</font>

248
00:14:05,525 --> 00:14:07,355
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you meddle...</font>

249
00:14:07,425 --> 00:14:10,885
<font color=#FFFF00>in broadcasting and politics? Why did you overstep your bounds?</font>

250
00:14:12,185 --> 00:14:13,625
<font color=#FFFF00>- This is terrible. - Stop.</font>

251
00:14:13,625 --> 00:14:14,625
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee Sook,</font>

252
00:14:15,255 --> 00:14:16,455
<font color=#FFFF00>do you want some ramyeon?</font>

253
00:14:16,855 --> 00:14:19,725
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon gave this pot to every one of the mountaineering club,</font>

254
00:14:20,785 --> 00:14:23,925
<font color=#FFFF00>and this is highly likely to be considered a bribe.</font>

255
00:14:25,655 --> 00:14:27,855
<font color=#FFFF00>- Why you... - This is unbelievable.</font>

256
00:14:28,155 --> 00:14:30,385
<font color=#FFFF00>- It's all done! - Honey...</font>

257
00:14:30,385 --> 00:14:32,755
<font color=#FFFF00>- Let's get divorced. - Honey.</font>

258
00:14:32,755 --> 00:14:35,825
<font color=#FFFF00>We should get divorced.</font>

259
00:14:36,155 --> 00:14:38,085
<font color=#FFFF00>So tell us honestly now!</font>

260
00:14:39,025 --> 00:14:42,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you get anything in return for raising illegal fund for Seonghan?</font>

261
00:14:42,655 --> 00:14:46,125
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't. I'm not lying.</font>

262
00:14:46,555 --> 00:14:48,585
<font color=#FFFF00>Then, how were you nominated by the Party's members?</font>

263
00:14:48,825 --> 00:14:52,325
<font color=#FFFF00>They voted for me only because I'm competent...</font>

264
00:14:52,485 --> 00:14:56,125
<font color=#FFFF00>and popular among the public.</font>

265
00:14:56,185 --> 00:14:57,925
<font color=#FFFF00>You're still out of your mind.</font>

266
00:14:59,285 --> 00:15:01,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop hitting me!</font>

267
00:15:01,885 --> 00:15:05,025
<font color=#FFFF00>It hurts! It hurts so bad!</font>

268
00:15:05,025 --> 00:15:08,825
<font color=#FFFF00>There's a possibility for you to be arrested...</font>

269
00:15:08,885 --> 00:15:11,325
<font color=#FFFF00>along with the officials of Minjeong Party and Seonghan Group.</font>

270
00:15:12,925 --> 00:15:15,155
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that true, Seong Hoon?</font>

271
00:15:15,485 --> 00:15:16,485
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell me the truth.</font>

272
00:15:17,385 --> 00:15:20,525
<font color=#FFFF00>- Did you ask them for help? - Well...</font>

273
00:15:25,055 --> 00:15:27,155
<font color=#FFFF00>It's about my brother.</font>

274
00:15:27,955 --> 00:15:30,755
<font color=#FFFF00>He runs a semiconductor manufacturer,</font>

275
00:15:30,855 --> 00:15:33,455
<font color=#FFFF00>and he wants to work with Seonghan again.</font>

276
00:15:34,125 --> 00:15:35,155
<font color=#FFFF00>Really?</font>

277
00:15:35,655 --> 00:15:38,855
<font color=#FFFF00>I wonder if you can help him resume the trade with Seonghan.</font>

278
00:15:40,655 --> 00:15:41,685
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

279
00:15:42,555 --> 00:15:46,225
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't. There's nothing like that at all.</font>

280
00:15:46,755 --> 00:15:47,785
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you sure?</font>

281
00:15:49,085 --> 00:15:51,055
<font color=#FFFF00>I am.</font>

282
00:15:52,425 --> 00:15:55,855
<font color=#FFFF00>Fine. You neither asked them for anything nor received anything.</font>

283
00:15:55,985 --> 00:15:57,385
<font color=#FFFF00>Right.</font>

284
00:15:59,055 --> 00:16:01,585
<font color=#FFFF00>- Exactly. - Don't be ridiculous.</font>

285
00:16:01,885 --> 00:16:05,355
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, it hurts so much. Darn it</font>

286
00:16:05,385 --> 00:16:07,225
<font color=#FFFF00>Then, why are you hiding now?</font>

287
00:16:10,055 --> 00:16:13,455
<font color=#FFFF00>- It's just for... - Tell us already!</font>

288
00:16:14,285 --> 00:16:17,785
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you sure? Are you really innocent?</font>

289
00:16:17,785 --> 00:16:21,885
<font color=#FFFF00>I am! I am really innocent!</font>

290
00:16:22,385 --> 00:16:26,285
<font color=#FFFF00>Why do you hit the same spot? It aches a lot.</font>

291
00:16:27,155 --> 00:16:29,985
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dad, it's me. - What is it?</font>

292
00:16:31,755 --> 00:16:33,825
<font color=#FFFF00>How is Mom?</font>

293
00:16:34,155 --> 00:16:35,925
<font color=#FFFF00>She's the same.</font>

294
00:16:36,525 --> 00:16:39,055
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm relieved since Seong Hoon...</font>

295
00:16:39,225 --> 00:16:42,155
<font color=#FFFF00>and Hee Sook are with Seong Sik in his office now.</font>

296
00:16:42,655 --> 00:16:45,485
<font color=#FFFF00>But I'm still worried about how things will turn out.</font>

297
00:16:45,855 --> 00:16:49,225
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't worry too much. Seong Sik is an honest person.</font>

298
00:16:49,525 --> 00:16:51,025
<font color=#FFFF00>It will be all right, Dad.</font>

299
00:16:51,625 --> 00:16:54,355
<font color=#FFFF00>- Do you feel better now? - Sorry?</font>

300
00:16:54,725 --> 00:16:58,055
<font color=#FFFF00>You were sweating this morning. Are you okay?</font>

301
00:16:59,825 --> 00:17:00,925
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm fine.</font>

302
00:17:01,355 --> 00:17:04,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Come home early. I'll make you invigorating tea.</font>

303
00:17:05,285 --> 00:17:06,285
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay.</font>

304
00:17:24,555 --> 00:17:27,355
<font color=#FFFF00>You want to protect your dad.</font>

305
00:17:28,085 --> 00:17:31,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. What did he do to him?</font>

306
00:17:33,755 --> 00:17:35,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you really not remember anything?</font>

307
00:17:36,125 --> 00:17:38,155
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it that you want to say?</font>

308
00:17:40,555 --> 00:17:42,255
<font color=#FFFF00>Your dad...</font>

309
00:17:43,155 --> 00:17:44,655
<font color=#FFFF00>is not your biological dad.</font>

310
00:17:45,195 --> 00:17:48,425
<font color=#FFFF00>He told the orphanage that he is your biological father.</font>

311
00:17:50,985 --> 00:17:52,025
<font color=#FFFF00>But he is not.</font>

312
00:17:52,955 --> 00:17:54,785
<font color=#FFFF00>He's a silly man.</font>

313
00:17:54,925 --> 00:17:56,885
<font color=#FFFF00>He fooled you completely.</font>

314
00:17:58,725 --> 00:18:02,655
<font color=#FFFF00>I guess you needed to believe that you were related to one of them.</font>

315
00:18:02,825 --> 00:18:05,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Only then, you would've endured your time there.</font>

316
00:18:06,755 --> 00:18:07,885
<font color=#FFFF00>What...</font>

317
00:18:09,255 --> 00:18:10,755
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you saying?</font>

318
00:18:11,155 --> 00:18:12,695
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll tell you one more thing.</font>

319
00:18:14,425 --> 00:18:17,985
<font color=#FFFF00>You shouldn't admire your father so much.</font>

320
00:18:19,255 --> 00:18:22,695
<font color=#FFFF00>He's not so admirable after all.</font>

321
00:18:35,455 --> 00:18:37,085
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it, Director Bang?</font>

322
00:18:41,855 --> 00:18:43,225
<font color=#FFFF00>Please come in, Director Han.</font>

323
00:18:46,225 --> 00:18:48,055
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hello. - Hi.</font>

324
00:18:48,755 --> 00:18:49,955
<font color=#FFFF00>How have you been?</font>

325
00:18:50,255 --> 00:18:51,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Please sit down, Director Han.</font>

326
00:18:51,925 --> 00:18:54,855
<font color=#FFFF00>President Lee came to discuss a few things with us. Please sit.</font>

327
00:18:56,025 --> 00:18:57,085
<font color=#FFFF00>All right.</font>

328
00:19:06,195 --> 00:19:07,225
<font color=#FFFF00>You...</font>

329
00:19:07,925 --> 00:19:09,455
<font color=#FFFF00>want to include a secret behind the character's birth?</font>

330
00:19:10,355 --> 00:19:12,285
<font color=#FFFF00>Why? Will it be a problem?</font>

331
00:19:13,355 --> 00:19:16,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Many Korean viewers like a plot with a secret behind someone's birth.</font>

332
00:19:17,585 --> 00:19:20,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Some may think it is out-dated,</font>

333
00:19:21,055 --> 00:19:24,585
<font color=#FFFF00>but we can't deny the fact that they do like it when it's in the plot.</font>

334
00:19:25,555 --> 00:19:28,585
<font color=#FFFF00>Besides, in order to export this to every country in Asia,</font>

335
00:19:28,655 --> 00:19:30,425
<font color=#FFFF00>this plot twist is an essential factor.</font>

336
00:19:31,925 --> 00:19:33,385
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you think so, Director Bang?</font>

337
00:19:34,825 --> 00:19:37,195
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, I agree with your assessment.</font>

338
00:19:38,255 --> 00:19:39,285
<font color=#FFFF00>However,</font>

339
00:19:40,355 --> 00:19:41,885
<font color=#FFFF00>this may be a bit over the line.</font>

340
00:19:46,825 --> 00:19:47,985
<font color=#FFFF00>Over the line?</font>

341
00:19:48,455 --> 00:19:50,225
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. I believe so.</font>

342
00:19:52,285 --> 00:19:54,125
<font color=#FFFF00>As you know, the genre of our drama is...</font>

343
00:19:54,825 --> 00:19:56,055
<font color=#FFFF00>romantic comedy.</font>

344
00:19:56,725 --> 00:19:58,255
<font color=#FFFF00>I am fully aware of that.</font>

345
00:19:59,355 --> 00:20:01,885
<font color=#FFFF00>However, this isn't an unreasonable demand.</font>

346
00:20:02,525 --> 00:20:04,885
<font color=#FFFF00>You can change the plot slightly.</font>

347
00:20:05,025 --> 00:20:06,585
<font color=#FFFF00>There are some things that...</font>

348
00:20:06,985 --> 00:20:09,255
<font color=#FFFF00>we can not give up on our end for the quality of the drama.</font>

349
00:20:09,755 --> 00:20:12,285
<font color=#FFFF00>If we ask the writer to do such a thing,</font>

350
00:20:12,385 --> 00:20:13,855
<font color=#FFFF00>you will put the writer in confusion.</font>

351
00:20:14,025 --> 00:20:16,255
<font color=#FFFF00>The whole storyline might go wrong.</font>

352
00:20:16,725 --> 00:20:20,225
<font color=#FFFF00>I personally believe a talented producer...</font>

353
00:20:20,525 --> 00:20:22,625
<font color=#FFFF00>creates the highest profits...</font>

354
00:20:22,825 --> 00:20:24,625
<font color=#FFFF00>without changing the writer's intention.</font>

355
00:20:31,455 --> 00:20:33,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't patronize me.</font>

356
00:20:34,425 --> 00:20:37,655
<font color=#FFFF00>- Pardon? - President Lee. What he meant...</font>

357
00:20:37,825 --> 00:20:39,925
<font color=#FFFF00>I am not trying to patronize you.</font>

358
00:20:40,225 --> 00:20:43,525
<font color=#FFFF00>In producing dramas, we have the upper hand from you.</font>

359
00:20:43,785 --> 00:20:46,625
<font color=#FFFF00>I meant you would trust us regarding the production of the drama.</font>

360
00:20:47,825 --> 00:20:49,195
<font color=#FFFF00>I understand where you are coming from.</font>

361
00:20:50,555 --> 00:20:53,985
<font color=#FFFF00>However, right now you are not making any profits.</font>

362
00:20:54,555 --> 00:20:56,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Isn't it better to make profits...</font>

363
00:20:56,925 --> 00:20:58,855
<font color=#FFFF00>by all means for your team...</font>

364
00:20:59,355 --> 00:21:01,885
<font color=#FFFF00>and for an investor like myself?</font>

365
00:21:04,825 --> 00:21:07,195
<font color=#FFFF00>Please add in a secret behind the character's birth...</font>

366
00:21:07,695 --> 00:21:10,255
<font color=#FFFF00>or I will personally meet the writer.</font>

367
00:21:24,385 --> 00:21:25,485
<font color=#FFFF00>President Lee.</font>

368
00:21:31,925 --> 00:21:33,085
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you doing this to us?</font>

369
00:21:34,385 --> 00:21:35,585
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't understand what you mean.</font>

370
00:21:36,055 --> 00:21:38,225
<font color=#FFFF00>You said you would trust and leave it to us.</font>

371
00:21:39,625 --> 00:21:40,655
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course.</font>

372
00:21:41,085 --> 00:21:42,785
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why I have invested in the production.</font>

373
00:21:43,355 --> 00:21:46,055
<font color=#FFFF00>However, once I start investing the money,</font>

374
00:21:46,555 --> 00:21:48,355
<font color=#FFFF00>I tend to worry in advance.</font>

375
00:21:49,125 --> 00:21:52,155
<font color=#FFFF00>- But still. - Do you think I am interfering?</font>

376
00:21:52,825 --> 00:21:54,985
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, I think so.</font>

377
00:21:55,955 --> 00:21:57,025
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry to hear that.</font>

378
00:21:57,755 --> 00:22:00,555
<font color=#FFFF00>From my perspective, under the contract,</font>

379
00:22:01,525 --> 00:22:03,955
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm merely exercising my right as an investor.</font>

380
00:22:05,185 --> 00:22:07,055
<font color=#FFFF00>I'd be grateful if you can understand.</font>

381
00:22:20,655 --> 00:22:22,825
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Oh Dong Hui. Did you make the presentation for this?</font>

382
00:22:23,555 --> 00:22:24,555
<font color=#FFFF00>No, it's not done.</font>

383
00:22:25,485 --> 00:22:28,125
<font color=#FFFF00>This is urgent. How could you have not finished this already?</font>

384
00:22:28,325 --> 00:22:29,485
<font color=#FFFF00>Hold on one second.</font>

385
00:22:30,455 --> 00:22:32,825
<font color=#FFFF00>- Mr. Park. Here's your coffee. - Thanks.</font>

386
00:22:33,525 --> 00:22:35,225
<font color=#FFFF00>I will finish it before I go home.</font>

387
00:22:35,225 --> 00:22:38,285
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Oh Dong Hui. Please finish your assignments in a timely manner.</font>

388
00:22:38,285 --> 00:22:41,255
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you know we're busy with new products for the upcoming season?</font>

389
00:22:45,285 --> 00:22:46,325
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

390
00:22:46,755 --> 00:22:48,285
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han. You are here.</font>

391
00:22:48,485 --> 00:22:49,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello, Sir.</font>

392
00:22:50,785 --> 00:22:53,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Oh Dong Hui. What are you doing here?</font>

393
00:22:53,825 --> 00:22:55,885
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sorry? - Why did you come to work?</font>

394
00:22:56,125 --> 00:22:57,155
<font color=#FFFF00>Shouldn't you be writing at home?</font>

395
00:22:57,855 --> 00:22:58,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Well...</font>

396
00:23:00,585 --> 00:23:02,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han. We are very busy, too.</font>

397
00:23:02,925 --> 00:23:05,185
<font color=#FFFF00>New products will be launching soon.</font>

398
00:23:05,455 --> 00:23:08,125
<font color=#FFFF00>It doesn't matter. She is a writer who has to write scripts.</font>

399
00:23:08,355 --> 00:23:10,355
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you make her do work like this?</font>

400
00:23:10,385 --> 00:23:11,625
<font color=#FFFF00>We didn't mean any harm.</font>

401
00:23:11,625 --> 00:23:13,185
<font color=#FFFF00>I told her to come to work.</font>

402
00:23:13,525 --> 00:23:14,785
<font color=#FFFF00>Whether she is a writer or not,</font>

403
00:23:15,025 --> 00:23:18,285
<font color=#FFFF00>the fact that she is our assistant hasn't changed.</font>

404
00:23:21,925 --> 00:23:24,055
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han. Can we have a moment?</font>

405
00:23:37,925 --> 00:23:40,925
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it this time? Did something happen?</font>

406
00:23:41,025 --> 00:23:42,225
<font color=#FFFF00>I have no clue.</font>

407
00:23:42,285 --> 00:23:44,685
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard the investor came to visit.</font>

408
00:23:44,755 --> 00:23:45,825
<font color=#FFFF00>The investor?</font>

409
00:23:47,385 --> 00:23:48,925
