<font color=#FFFF00>That's what I'm saying. Ask her to do it when she comes back.</font>

615
00:38:39,125 --> 00:38:40,225
<font color=#FFFF00>You can't do that.</font>

616
00:38:40,555 --> 00:38:42,785
<font color=#FFFF00>Once a mom, always a mom. You're my mom, too.</font>

617
00:38:42,855 --> 00:38:43,955
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

618
00:38:44,595 --> 00:38:45,595
<font color=#FFFF00>Look.</font>

619
00:38:45,885 --> 00:38:47,855
<font color=#FFFF00>I have to memorize these lyrics.</font>

620
00:38:48,055 --> 00:38:50,225
<font color=#FFFF00>Could you bring me a cup of water?</font>

621
00:38:51,785 --> 00:38:52,855
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

622
00:38:59,925 --> 00:39:02,685
<font color=#FFFF00>Listen up, everyone!</font>

623
00:39:03,955 --> 00:39:08,355
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee Sook isn't home right now.</font>

624
00:39:08,825 --> 00:39:11,055
<font color=#FFFF00>If you don't want to study, don't study.</font>

625
00:39:11,125 --> 00:39:14,455
<font color=#FFFF00>If you want water, get it yourself with your own hands.</font>

626
00:39:14,925 --> 00:39:16,095
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you understand?</font>

627
00:39:17,285 --> 00:39:18,425
<font color=#FFFF00>You'd better...</font>

628
00:39:18,855 --> 00:39:20,755
<font color=#FFFF00>stay quiet today.</font>

629
00:39:21,955 --> 00:39:25,325
<font color=#FFFF00>I will give you a good scolding if you upset me in any way!</font>

630
00:39:32,455 --> 00:39:33,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello?</font>

631
00:39:39,355 --> 00:39:40,425
<font color=#FFFF00>A piano?</font>

632
00:39:42,685 --> 00:39:43,985
<font color=#FFFF00>The chest?</font>

633
00:39:45,655 --> 00:39:47,185
<font color=#FFFF00>Sir!</font>

634
00:39:47,225 --> 00:39:50,285
<font color=#FFFF00>I never said I wanted to sell this!</font>

635
00:39:50,285 --> 00:39:53,055
<font color=#FFFF00>We've already closed the bargain, Ma'am.</font>

636
00:39:53,055 --> 00:39:55,225
<font color=#FFFF00>That's not important right now!</font>

637
00:39:55,225 --> 00:39:57,325
<font color=#FFFF00>We're taking this chest in exchange...</font>

638
00:39:57,325 --> 00:39:59,485
<font color=#FFFF00>for a discount on the piano. I told you already. See?</font>

639
00:39:59,485 --> 00:40:01,925
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't care. You can't take this!</font>

640
00:40:01,925 --> 00:40:03,825
<font color=#FFFF00>- Let's go. - No. You can't do this.</font>

641
00:40:03,825 --> 00:40:05,885
<font color=#FFFF00>- Let it go, Ma'am. - No! Put it down!</font>

642
00:40:05,885 --> 00:40:06,885
<font color=#FFFF00>Put it down!</font>

643
00:40:07,155 --> 00:40:09,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Put it down, Sir! Hey!</font>

644
00:40:21,885 --> 00:40:23,385
<font color=#FFFF00>- Is it fun, Ah In? - Yes.</font>

645
00:40:23,555 --> 00:40:25,255
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you play the piano now, Chang Soo?</font>

646
00:40:25,255 --> 00:40:27,955
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. I should learn how to play the piano...</font>

647
00:40:27,985 --> 00:40:29,555
<font color=#FFFF00>to become a great opera singer.</font>

648
00:40:38,725 --> 00:40:39,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

649
00:40:40,625 --> 00:40:42,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Put Hee Sook on the phone right now.</font>

650
00:40:43,025 --> 00:40:44,425
<font color=#FFFF00>She's there, isn't she?</font>

651
00:40:45,385 --> 00:40:46,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Really?</font>

652
00:40:47,185 --> 00:40:50,055
<font color=#FFFF00>Did she really sell your chest without talking to you about it?</font>

653
00:40:50,125 --> 00:40:52,225
<font color=#FFFF00>My goodness.</font>

654
00:40:54,095 --> 00:40:55,285
<font color=#FFFF00>I took a day off...</font>

655
00:40:55,525 --> 00:40:58,555
<font color=#FFFF00>and stayed home because the kids are on their spring vacation.</font>

656
00:40:58,725 --> 00:41:01,225
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee Sook sent guys to take...</font>

657
00:41:01,555 --> 00:41:04,725
<font color=#FFFF00>my chest, the article that my parents left me.</font>

658
00:41:04,885 --> 00:41:06,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Put her on the phone now.</font>

659
00:41:06,385 --> 00:41:09,095
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm going to kill her today.</font>

660
00:41:11,055 --> 00:41:14,385
<font color=#FFFF00>She disguised herself as the cafe owner...</font>

661
00:41:14,925 --> 00:41:16,185
<font color=#FFFF00>and went out to buy food.</font>

662
00:41:16,755 --> 00:41:18,055
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, what?</font>

663
00:41:19,955 --> 00:41:21,625
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't believe her.</font>

664
00:41:24,285 --> 00:41:26,285
<font color=#FFFF00>You should come home, then.</font>

665
00:41:26,285 --> 00:41:29,655
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm too upset that I'm going crazy here.</font>

666
00:41:30,555 --> 00:41:32,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Hye Joo. I know how you feel,</font>

667
00:41:32,595 --> 00:41:35,025
<font color=#FFFF00>but I can't just leave right now.</font>

668
00:41:35,055 --> 00:41:38,025
<font color=#FFFF00>What does it have to do with you? You can just leave!</font>

669
00:41:39,155 --> 00:41:41,485
<font color=#FFFF00>Well... Actually,</font>

670
00:41:43,055 --> 00:41:45,685
<font color=#FFFF00>it's partly my fault that this happened to Seong Sik.</font>

671
00:41:46,755 --> 00:41:47,825
<font color=#FFFF00>Why is it your fault?</font>

672
00:41:48,485 --> 00:41:51,255
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know Reporter Yim from Jinsung Daily News I worked with?</font>

673
00:41:52,425 --> 00:41:53,985
<font color=#FFFF00>He came to see me a few days ago.</font>

674
00:41:54,595 --> 00:41:56,685
<font color=#FFFF00>He asked me for documents on the corrupt relationship...</font>

675
00:41:56,855 --> 00:41:59,595
<font color=#FFFF00>between Minjeong Party and Seonghan Group, so I gave them to him.</font>

676
00:42:00,125 --> 00:42:02,955
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Sik of all people got involved in it.</font>

677
00:42:04,225 --> 00:42:05,225
<font color=#FFFF00>Really?</font>

678
00:42:06,825 --> 00:42:09,625
<font color=#FFFF00>It's driving me crazy now.</font>

679
00:42:10,285 --> 00:42:11,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Hoon.</font>

680
00:42:16,625 --> 00:42:18,925
<font color=#FFFF00>What did you just say, Seong Hoon?</font>

681
00:42:20,055 --> 00:42:21,125
<font color=#FFFF00>When did you get back?</font>

682
00:42:21,325 --> 00:42:23,095
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you say...</font>

683
00:42:23,595 --> 00:42:25,955
<font color=#FFFF00>you handed over documents to Jinsung Daily News?</font>

684
00:42:27,255 --> 00:42:28,725
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me explain, Seong Sik.</font>

685
00:42:28,725 --> 00:42:31,725
<font color=#FFFF00>How... How could you do this to me, Seong Hoon?</font>

686
00:42:32,595 --> 00:42:36,655
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you do this to your brother? How could you?</font>

687
00:42:37,125 --> 00:42:39,455
<font color=#FFFF00>- How? - Wait, Seong Sik.</font>

688
00:42:39,685 --> 00:42:42,355
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Sik. What's wrong?</font>

689
00:42:43,485 --> 00:42:45,955
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you do this to me?</font>

690
00:42:45,955 --> 00:42:47,655
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Hoon. Why is he doing this?</font>

691
00:42:47,655 --> 00:42:49,825
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong, Seong Sik? Let go of him first.</font>

692
00:42:49,825 --> 00:42:50,855
<font color=#FFFF00>Get off of me.</font>

693
00:42:51,985 --> 00:42:53,485
<font color=#FFFF00>How could you...</font>

694
00:42:54,655 --> 00:42:57,185
<font color=#FFFF00>help people ruin your brother?</font>

695
00:42:58,025 --> 00:42:59,455
<font color=#FFFF00>What kind of a person does that?</font>

696
00:43:00,055 --> 00:43:01,655
<font color=#FFFF00>Who does that?</font>

697
00:43:01,655 --> 00:43:04,255
<font color=#FFFF00>- Who? - It's not that, Seong Sik.</font>

698
00:43:04,255 --> 00:43:05,595
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me explain.</font>

699
00:43:05,595 --> 00:43:06,625
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Hoon!</font>

700
00:43:07,055 --> 00:43:09,625
<font color=#FFFF00>- Seong Hoon! - I'm sorry.</font>

701
00:43:09,725 --> 00:43:10,855
<font color=#FFFF00>How can this be?</font>

702
00:43:15,025 --> 00:43:16,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Hwang.</font>

703
00:43:16,485 --> 00:43:19,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Why don't you get up and eat some porridge?</font>

704
00:43:19,825 --> 00:43:21,555
<font color=#FFFF00>No. I don't want to eat anything.</font>

705
00:43:21,625 --> 00:43:24,655
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on now. Please get up.</font>

706
00:43:24,725 --> 00:43:25,955
<font color=#FFFF00>- Gosh. - Here.</font>

707
00:43:28,595 --> 00:43:30,095
<font color=#FFFF00>Everything tastes bitter.</font>

708
00:43:30,855 --> 00:43:34,155
<font color=#FFFF00>My grandson is on the front page of the newspaper...</font>

709
00:43:34,325 --> 00:43:36,685
<font color=#FFFF00>for doing something bad.</font>

710
00:43:36,685 --> 00:43:39,855
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm his grandmother. How can I be eating now?</font>

711
00:43:40,625 --> 00:43:44,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't say that. You should eat.</font>

712
00:43:45,025 --> 00:43:48,825
<font color=#FFFF00>Well, it's not something so terrible.</font>

713
00:43:49,085 --> 00:43:51,185
<font color=#FFFF00>He wasn't arrested or anything.</font>

714
00:43:51,485 --> 00:43:52,785
<font color=#FFFF00>Arrested?</font>

715
00:43:53,285 --> 00:43:56,225
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you say that?</font>

716
00:43:56,355 --> 00:43:58,285
<font color=#FFFF00>What I'm trying to say is...</font>

717
00:43:58,285 --> 00:44:01,955
<font color=#FFFF00>it may turn out to be something not so serious.</font>

718
00:44:02,355 --> 00:44:06,155
<font color=#FFFF00>Sometimes you get into trouble,</font>

719
00:44:06,255 --> 00:44:09,825
<font color=#FFFF00>and sometimes you have bad things happen to you.</font>

720
00:44:10,225 --> 00:44:13,255
<font color=#FFFF00>Besides, your second grandson was on...</font>

721
00:44:13,255 --> 00:44:14,785
<font color=#FFFF00>many TV shows.</font>

722
00:44:14,785 --> 00:44:18,525
<font color=#FFFF00>He has been on everyone's lips.</font>

723
00:44:18,525 --> 00:44:20,225
<font color=#FFFF00>That's what I'm saying.</font>

724
00:44:20,225 --> 00:44:22,585
<font color=#FFFF00>He always has been so fond of the limelight.</font>

725
00:44:22,585 --> 00:44:25,485
<font color=#FFFF00>I knew something like this would happen to him someday.</font>

726
00:44:27,525 --> 00:44:30,255
<font color=#FFFF00>My goodness. Ms. Hwang.</font>

727
00:44:30,455 --> 00:44:32,955
<font color=#FFFF00>Please calm down.</font>

728
00:44:36,655 --> 00:44:37,955
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm going out.</font>

729
00:44:38,455 --> 00:44:41,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Please eat the porridge when you feel better.</font>

730
00:44:42,085 --> 00:44:43,855
<font color=#FFFF00>We're old women.</font>

731
00:44:43,855 --> 00:44:46,325
<font color=#FFFF00>If we worry too much, we will soon die.</font>

732
00:44:47,785 --> 00:44:50,825
<font color=#FFFF00>Please try to ease your mind, okay?</font>

733
00:45:05,555 --> 00:45:07,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you Ms. Oh Dong Hui?</font>

734
00:45:07,685 --> 00:45:08,885
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, President Bang.</font>

735
00:45:09,985 --> 00:45:11,155
<font color=#FFFF00>I see.</font>

736
00:45:11,425 --> 00:45:14,225
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard you were signing the contract today.</font>

737
00:45:14,255 --> 00:45:17,325
<font color=#FFFF00>I just called you here to meet you. Don't be scared.</font>

738
00:45:18,585 --> 00:45:19,955
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not, Sir.</font>

739
00:45:21,385 --> 00:45:24,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Your grandmother is Ms. Oh Gui Boon, right?</font>

740
00:45:26,085 --> 00:45:27,985
<font color=#FFFF00>How do you know my grandmother?</font>

741
00:45:30,125 --> 00:45:33,555
<font color=#FFFF00>I grew up eating the food your grandmother made.</font>

742
00:45:37,285 --> 00:45:38,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you?</font>

743
00:45:38,955 --> 00:45:40,855
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't know.</font>

744
00:45:42,085 --> 00:45:45,155
<font color=#FFFF00>I guess she didn't tell you. That's disappointing.</font>

745
00:45:46,985 --> 00:45:48,685
<font color=#FFFF00>You're her granddaughter,</font>

746
00:45:49,625 --> 00:45:52,155
<font color=#FFFF00>so that'd make you my niece.</font>

747
00:45:53,855 --> 00:45:56,625
<font color=#FFFF00>You can relax. Treat me like your uncle.</font>

748
00:45:58,725 --> 00:45:59,725
<font color=#FFFF00>Pardon?</font>

749
00:46:01,625 --> 00:46:04,555
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard both of your parents passed away.</font>

750
00:46:04,755 --> 00:46:08,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. They died when I was little.</font>

751
00:46:08,155 --> 00:46:10,725
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why my grandmother raised me.</font>

752
00:46:11,485 --> 00:46:13,285
<font color=#FFFF00>You look much better in person.</font>

753
00:46:14,225 --> 00:46:17,555
<font color=#FFFF00>You don't resemble your grandmother at all.</font>

754
00:46:19,685 --> 00:46:21,025
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way,</font>

755
00:46:21,855 --> 00:46:24,155
<font color=#FFFF00>you somehow look familiar to me.</font>

756
00:46:25,485 --> 00:46:27,155
<font color=#FFFF00>My grandmother...</font>

757
00:46:27,155 --> 00:46:29,725
<font color=#FFFF00>always told me that I look just like my mother.</font>

758
00:46:33,125 --> 00:46:34,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that so?</font>

759
00:46:36,355 --> 00:46:37,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you...</font>

760
00:46:37,925 --> 00:46:41,455
<font color=#FFFF00>know my parents well, by any chance?</font>

761
00:46:42,855 --> 00:46:45,385
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not sure about that.</font>

762
00:46:46,355 --> 00:46:50,225
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know if your parents are the ones I knew or not.</font>

763
00:46:52,385 --> 00:46:54,785
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyhow, congratulations on becoming...</font>

764
00:46:54,925 --> 00:46:56,525
<font color=#FFFF00>our company's scriptwriter.</font>

765
00:46:56,755 --> 00:46:57,885
<font color=#FFFF00>I hope to see you often.</font>

766
00:46:59,785 --> 00:47:01,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, Sir.</font>

767
00:47:22,955 --> 00:47:25,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui. Can I talk to you for a second?</font>

768
00:47:38,255 --> 00:47:41,355
<font color=#FFFF00>Why didn't Director Han come to work today? Is everything okay?</font>

769
00:47:41,585 --> 00:47:42,655
<font color=#FFFF00>Sorry?</font>

770
00:47:43,925 --> 00:47:45,585
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not sure why he didn't.</font>

771
00:47:45,785 --> 00:47:47,825
<font color=#FFFF00>Didn't you two come to work together?</font>

772
00:47:48,325 --> 00:47:51,125
<font color=#FFFF00>You don't like us coming to work together.</font>

773
00:47:51,285 --> 00:47:53,155
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you messing with me right now?</font>

774
00:47:53,225 --> 00:47:54,585
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you have to push ahead...</font>

775
00:47:54,785 --> 00:47:56,685
<font color=#FFFF00>to include a secret behind the character's birth?</font>

776
00:47:57,055 --> 00:47:58,125
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

777
00:47:58,425 --> 00:48:01,185
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han had a hard time because of it.</font>

778
00:48:01,355 --> 00:48:04,755
<font color=#FFFF00>You know better than anyone that he hates those things.</font>

779
00:48:06,425 --> 00:48:09,325
<font color=#FFFF00>What about you? What do you think?</font>

780
00:48:10,555 --> 00:48:13,725
<font color=#FFFF00>I guess we can include it when it's absolutely necessary,</font>

781
00:48:14,025 --> 00:48:16,855
<font color=#FFFF00>but I'm opposed to it if it's merely for the ratings.</font>

782
00:48:16,955 --> 00:48:20,325
<font color=#FFFF00>There must be a reason why we have to have such a setting.</font>

783
00:48:20,955 --> 00:48:23,055
<font color=#FFFF00>You've become so arrogant.</font>

784
00:48:23,485 --> 00:48:27,385
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think you're a sought-after writer or something? Listen.</font>

785
00:48:28,155 --> 00:48:30,025
<font color=#FFFF00>If we fail to attract investors, Director Han will be fired.</font>

786
00:48:31,125 --> 00:48:33,125
<font color=#FFFF00>If that's not what you want,</font>

787
00:48:33,255 --> 00:48:35,355
<font color=#FFFF00>you'd better think about it again.</font>

788
00:48:58,055 --> 00:48:59,055
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom,</font>

789
00:49:00,185 --> 00:49:01,425
<font color=#FFFF00>I really didn't know...</font>

790
00:49:02,725 --> 00:49:05,785
<font color=#FFFF00>you'd gladly say okay and come here.</font>

791
00:49:07,125 --> 00:49:08,785
<font color=#FFFF00>House chores are...</font>

792
00:49:08,855 --> 00:49:11,785
<font color=#FFFF00>much better than cleaning apartment buildings.</font>

793
00:49:11,855 --> 00:49:13,255
<font color=#FFFF00>That's right.</font>

794
00:49:14,685 --> 00:49:16,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Now that you're here,</font>

795
00:49:17,425 --> 00:49:19,655
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel like we've gone back to the old days.</font>

796
00:49:20,985 --> 00:49:22,625
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm glad to hear that.</font>

797
00:49:24,355 --> 00:49:27,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Where are you going? Please take a seat.</font>

798
00:49:28,185 --> 00:49:31,955
<font color=#FFFF00>You stayed until we finish our meals...</font>

799
00:49:32,185 --> 00:49:33,485
<font color=#FFFF00>and served more side dishes as well.</font>

800
00:49:39,585 --> 00:49:41,685
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's not talk about the past.</font>

801
00:49:42,955 --> 00:49:44,055
<font color=#FFFF00>Why not?</font>

802
00:49:46,825 --> 00:49:48,355
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it because it reminds you of Gwang Ho?</font>

803
00:49:51,485 --> 00:49:52,555
<font color=#FFFF00>You know...</font>

804
00:49:53,855 --> 00:49:55,125
<font color=#FFFF00>Gwang Ho is dead, right?</font>

805
00:49:57,085 --> 00:49:58,125
<font color=#FFFF00>I do.</font>

806
00:50:00,425 --> 00:50:01,855
<font color=#FFFF00>How did you know that?</font>

807
00:50:02,885 --> 00:50:06,455
<font color=#FFFF00>It's been reported in newspapers. He had a boat accident.</font>

808
00:50:07,025 --> 00:50:09,025
<font color=#FFFF00>That's right. You saw it in newspapers.</font>

809
00:50:10,185 --> 00:50:11,425
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way,</font>

810
00:50:12,725 --> 00:50:14,885
<font color=#FFFF00>you didn't come to his funeral, did you?</font>

811
00:50:15,985 --> 00:50:19,725
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you my life was too hectic at that time.</font>

812
00:50:19,985 --> 00:50:21,955
<font color=#FFFF00>That's nonsense.</font>

813
00:50:22,425 --> 00:50:25,385
<font color=#FFFF00>You favoured Gwang Ho a lot more than me.</font>

814
00:50:26,625 --> 00:50:29,855
<font color=#FFFF00>When did I favor Gwang Ho more?</font>

815
00:50:30,385 --> 00:50:31,685
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you sure you didn't?</font>

816
00:50:32,825 --> 00:50:34,585
<font color=#FFFF00>President and you...</font>

817
00:50:35,025 --> 00:50:37,755
<font color=#FFFF00>loved him more than you loved me.</font>

818
00:50:38,985 --> 00:50:42,125
<font color=#FFFF00>You didn't pay attention to me at all.</font>

819
00:50:42,425 --> 00:50:44,325
<font color=#FFFF00>That's not true.</font>

820
00:50:45,055 --> 00:50:47,725
<font color=#FFFF00>If you keep saying such nonsense,</font>

821
00:50:48,185 --> 00:50:51,255
<font color=#FFFF00>- I won't come here anymore. - You won't come here?</font>

822
00:50:53,825 --> 00:50:57,655
<font color=#FFFF00>I know you came here for a reason.</font>

823
00:51:00,155 --> 00:51:02,185
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean by that?</font>

824
00:51:03,055 --> 00:51:06,585
<font color=#FFFF00>I called you and visited you so often,</font>

825
00:51:06,625 --> 00:51:08,485
<font color=#FFFF00>so you decided to have a close watch...</font>

826
00:51:08,825 --> 00:51:11,855
<font color=#FFFF00>on me here, while avoiding unnecessary misunderstandings.</font>

827
00:51:12,325 --> 00:51:13,725
<font color=#FFFF00>Isn't that why you're here?</font>

828
00:51:13,855 --> 00:51:16,655
<font color=#FFFF00>What... What did you say?</font>

829
00:51:16,825 --> 00:51:17,955
<font color=#FFFF00>Or...</font>

830
00:51:19,185 --> 00:51:21,425
<font color=#FFFF00>are you here because you miss my mother...</font>

831
00:51:21,655 --> 00:51:23,785
<font color=#FFFF00>who's gone missing?</font>

832
00:51:24,555 --> 00:51:26,625
<font color=#FFFF00>What on earth are you talking about?</font>

833
00:51:27,985 --> 00:51:30,485
<font color=#FFFF00>It doesn't matter. I live alone since my wife died.</font>

834
00:51:30,655 --> 00:51:32,725
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm happy to be with you here.</font>

835
00:51:34,655 --> 00:51:37,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom, please put some egg on it.</font>

836
00:51:39,125 --> 00:51:41,485
<font color=#FFFF00>Please, Mom.</font>

837
00:51:41,685 --> 00:51:45,885
<font color=#FFFF00>I want to eat it. Please.</font>

838
00:52:26,225 --> 00:52:28,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han, are you in?</font>

839
00:52:29,585 --> 00:52:30,625
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you in?</font>

840
00:52:30,925 --> 00:52:33,985
<font color=#FFFF00>Why does Seong Sik make me worried all the time?</font>

841
00:52:37,855 --> 00:52:39,125
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui.</font>

842
00:52:40,425 --> 00:52:42,285
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing there?</font>

843
00:52:47,455 --> 00:52:49,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you knocking...</font>

844
00:52:49,325 --> 00:52:52,085
<font color=#FFFF00>on the door of Seong Joon's room at this late hour?</font>

845
00:52:52,355 --> 00:52:56,085
<font color=#FFFF00>I have something to tell him.</font>

846
00:52:56,285 --> 00:52:58,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon is still at work.</font>

847
00:53:01,455 --> 00:53:04,255
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay. I am sorry.</font>

848
00:53:05,655 --> 00:53:06,955
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui,</font>

849
00:53:07,325 --> 00:53:10,285
<font color=#FFFF00>enough is enough.</font>

850
00:53:11,155 --> 00:53:14,525
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sorry? - Do you know what happened to us?</font>

851
00:53:15,055 --> 00:53:18,885
<font color=#FFFF00>Everyone of my family is anxious and disturbed at this moment.</font>

852
00:53:18,885 --> 00:53:22,425
<font color=#FFFF00>And do you want to fool around in Seong Joon's room that badly?</font>

853
00:53:22,725 --> 00:53:25,955
<font color=#FFFF00>- I just... - Be quiet. I don't want excuses!</font>

854
00:53:26,255 --> 00:53:30,155
<font color=#FFFF00>You're living off us now. Then, you should behave at least!</font>

855
00:53:30,385 --> 00:53:33,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you so slow-witted? Are you a kid?</font>

856
00:53:34,455 --> 00:53:37,325
<font color=#FFFF00>I apologize. I'm so sorry.</font>

857
00:54:24,585 --> 00:54:27,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Both the broadcasting station and my company liked the scenario...</font>

858
00:54:27,885 --> 00:54:30,455
<font color=#FFFF00>because it isn't clichéd at all...</font>

859
00:54:30,525 --> 00:54:32,085
<font color=#FFFF00>and unique.</font>

860
00:54:32,625 --> 00:54:35,725
<font color=#FFFF00>We cannot get rid of such charms.</font>

861
00:54:37,755 --> 00:54:39,385
<font color=#FFFF00>Why do you not like it?</font>

862
00:54:41,755 --> 00:54:44,155
<font color=#FFFF00>You also have a secret behind your birth.</font>

863
00:54:48,155 --> 00:54:50,455
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you trying to tell me?</font>

864
00:54:50,725 --> 00:54:52,755
<font color=#FFFF00>I thought we'd speak the same language...</font>

865
00:54:53,385 --> 00:54:55,255
<font color=#FFFF00>as we both were raised in an orphanage.</font>

866
00:54:56,355 --> 00:54:59,425
<font color=#FFFF00>A man encounters a wrongful death...</font>

867
00:54:59,625 --> 00:55:01,325
<font color=#FFFF00>and leaves his two sons.</font>

868
00:55:02,785 --> 00:55:05,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Since then, the two sons are separated...</font>

869
00:55:06,455 --> 00:55:08,785
<font color=#FFFF00>from each other for more than 20 years,</font>

870
00:55:09,385 --> 00:55:12,055
<font color=#FFFF00>unable to know whether their brother is still alive.</font>

871
00:55:12,855 --> 00:55:15,455
<font color=#FFFF00>One of them is looking for his brother,</font>

872
00:55:16,125 --> 00:55:18,155
<font color=#FFFF00>but it's not easy at all.</font>

873
00:55:20,055 --> 00:55:22,225
<font color=#FFFF00>If the other one also had tried to find his brother,</font>

874
00:55:22,685 --> 00:55:24,685
<font color=#FFFF00>they might have been able to meet earlier.</font>

875
00:55:25,525 --> 00:55:28,155
<font color=#FFFF00>Isn't it dramatic?</font>

876
00:55:29,455 --> 00:55:30,485
<font color=#FFFF00>Mr. Lee,</font>

877
00:55:31,085 --> 00:55:34,455
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry about your private matter.</font>

878
00:55:35,855 --> 00:55:38,985
<font color=#FFFF00>Yet, bringing it to the plot is unacceptable.</font>

879
00:55:39,225 --> 00:55:41,055
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you...</font>

880
00:55:41,925 --> 00:55:44,985
<font color=#FFFF00>what investors expect. I invested my money,</font>

881
00:55:45,185 --> 00:55:47,225
<font color=#FFFF00>then it should produce good results.</font>

882
00:55:47,925 --> 00:55:51,525
<font color=#FFFF00>That's how I'm able to run a world-class investment company.</font>

883
00:55:55,655 --> 00:55:59,155
<font color=#FFFF00>I thought you were polite and sincere,</font>

884
00:55:59,785 --> 00:56:00,785
<font color=#FFFF00>but I was wrong.</font>

885
00:56:01,525 --> 00:56:05,455
<font color=#FFFF00>You privately hired your in-law who lives in your rooftop as a writer.</font>

886
00:56:05,685 --> 00:56:07,825
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't hire her because she's my in-law.</font>

887
00:56:08,585 --> 00:56:10,455
<font color=#FFFF00>You would know if you read her scenario.</font>

888
00:56:10,725 --> 00:56:13,985
<font color=#FFFF00>There are countless writers who can write like her.</font>

889
00:56:15,185 --> 00:56:16,185
<font color=#FFFF00>I think...</font>

890
00:56:17,185 --> 00:56:19,525
<font color=#FFFF00>you failed to put your personal feelings aside.</font>

891
00:56:21,185 --> 00:56:22,625
<font color=#FFFF00>That's not true.</font>

892
00:56:23,225 --> 00:56:24,285
<font color=#FFFF00>Moreover,</font>

893
00:56:24,855 --> 00:56:27,225
<font color=#FFFF00>you visit an investor without making an appointment...</font>

894
00:56:27,625 --> 00:56:30,385
<font color=#FFFF00>and complain about his decision without presenting any base data.</font>

895
00:56:32,725 --> 00:56:35,255
<font color=#FFFF00>You were raised by a father who only cares about his children...</font>

896
00:56:36,055 --> 00:56:37,655
<font color=#FFFF00>and spent a comfortable childhood.</font>

897
00:56:38,725 --> 00:56:42,225
<font color=#FFFF00>- I guess that's why you're rude. - If you felt that way, I apologize.</font>

898
00:56:43,325 --> 00:56:45,655
<font color=#FFFF00>But you've crossed the line.</font>

899
00:56:47,455 --> 00:56:48,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Why?</font>

900
00:56:49,685 --> 00:56:52,055
<font color=#FFFF00>Did I offend you by mentioning your father?</font>

901
00:56:52,525 --> 00:56:54,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, you did.</font>

902
00:56:56,325 --> 00:56:59,585
<font color=#FFFF00>But I know quite a lot about your father.</font>

903
00:57:02,755 --> 00:57:05,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Everyone has their dark side.</font>

904
00:57:05,985 --> 00:57:09,325
<font color=#FFFF00>- What are you talking about? - All fathers have...</font>

905
00:57:10,025 --> 00:57:12,685
<font color=#FFFF00>their own ugly side they want to hide...</font>

906
00:57:13,985 --> 00:57:15,655
<font color=#FFFF00>from their children.</font>

907
00:57:17,555 --> 00:57:20,655
<font color=#FFFF00>And your father is no different.</font>

908
00:57:44,525 --> 00:57:46,025
<font color=#FFFF00>We need to meet now.</font>

909
00:58:01,085 --> 00:58:02,085
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness.</font>

910
00:58:02,425 --> 00:58:04,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Why didn't you call me earlier?</font>

911
00:58:04,055 --> 00:58:07,255
<font color=#FFFF00>I stayed here all day long to decide the location of my store.</font>

912
00:58:07,485 --> 00:58:11,025
<font color=#FFFF00>We could've had dinner together if you had called me earlier.</font>

913
00:58:20,955 --> 00:58:22,885
<font color=#FFFF00>I called you because I have a few questions.</font>

914
00:58:23,085 --> 00:58:24,185
<font color=#FFFF00>A question?</font>

915
00:58:24,685 --> 00:58:25,755
<font color=#FFFF00>What's that?</font>

916
00:58:29,425 --> 00:58:30,485
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you...</font>

917
00:58:31,985 --> 00:58:33,625
<font color=#FFFF00>my birth mother?</font>

918
00:58:35,955 --> 00:58:36,955
<font color=#FFFF00>What did you say?</font>

919
00:58:37,055 --> 00:58:38,185
<font color=#FFFF00>Please answer me.</font>

920
00:58:38,425 --> 00:58:40,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, you're such a rude brat.</font>

921
00:58:41,055 --> 00:58:44,355
<font color=#FFFF00>It took a long time for you to ask that question.</font>

922
00:58:45,125 --> 00:58:47,055
<font color=#FFFF00>Just tell me the truth.</font>

923
00:58:47,325 --> 00:58:48,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, how scary.</font>

924
00:58:49,085 --> 00:58:51,355
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm too scared to tell you the truth.</font>

925
00:58:59,985 --> 00:59:01,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Listen.</font>

926
00:59:01,855 --> 00:59:03,955
<font color=#FFFF00>I assumed it when you just left without a word...</font>

927
00:59:03,955 --> 00:59:06,825
<font color=#FFFF00>after giving me the money. You shouldn't be like this.</font>

928
00:59:07,255 --> 00:59:09,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Your late father will resent you.</font>

929
00:59:11,685 --> 00:59:12,885
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

930
00:59:13,155 --> 00:59:15,485
<font color=#FFFF00>I said your late father will resent you.</font>

931
00:59:17,125 --> 00:59:18,825
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know my birth father?</font>

932
00:59:19,555 --> 00:59:20,655
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course.</font>

933
00:59:21,555 --> 00:59:24,525
<font color=#FFFF00>When you were little, your father brought you to my store...</font>

934
00:59:24,525 --> 00:59:26,255
<font color=#FFFF00>whenever he wanted to drink.</font>

935
00:59:26,385 --> 00:59:29,285
<font color=#FFFF00>No. I only have one father.</font>

936
00:59:29,485 --> 00:59:31,225
<font color=#FFFF00>That's what I've always believed.</font>

937
00:59:31,555 --> 00:59:34,985
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why the father you have now is such a bad man.</font>

938
00:59:35,455 --> 00:59:38,085
<font color=#FFFF00>He deceived you completely.</font>

939
00:59:38,325 --> 00:59:39,385
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know that?</font>

940
00:59:59,025 --> 01:00:00,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han.</font>

941
01:00:09,255 --> 01:00:12,585
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong? Did something happen to you today?</font>

942
01:00:38,125 --> 01:00:42,185
<font color=#FFFF00>I think I can include a secret behind the character's birth.</font>

943
01:00:42,525 --> 01:00:44,555
<font color=#FFFF00>I've given it some thought.</font>

944
01:00:44,825 --> 01:00:45,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui.</font>

945
01:00:47,655 --> 01:00:49,525
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

946
01:00:50,985 --> 01:00:52,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Nothing.</font>

947
01:00:53,925 --> 01:00:54,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Never mind.</font>

948
01:00:57,085 --> 01:01:00,155
<font color=#FFFF00>What's the matter? What is it?</font>

949
01:01:05,425 --> 01:01:06,525
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

950
01:01:11,655 --> 01:01:12,755
<font color=#FFFF00>I was...</font>

951
01:01:14,385 --> 01:01:16,255
<font color=#FFFF00>adopted by this family when I was seven.</font>

952
01:01:19,625 --> 01:01:20,825
<font color=#FFFF00>Up until now,</font>

953
01:01:21,625 --> 01:01:24,525
<font color=#FFFF00>I thought I was a child my father had with another woman.</font>

954
01:01:25,785 --> 01:01:26,825
<font color=#FFFF00>No.</font>

955
01:01:28,955 --> 01:01:30,985
<font color=#FFFF00>To be exact, I chose...</font>

956
01:01:31,455 --> 01:01:32,585
<font color=#FFFF00>to believe that.</font>

957
01:01:34,285 --> 01:01:36,825
<font color=#FFFF00>How could that be?</font>

958
01:01:37,725 --> 01:01:39,655
<font color=#FFFF00>There hasn't been any problem so far.</font>

959
01:01:40,685 --> 01:01:41,885
<font color=#FFFF00>I've been happy.</font>

960
01:01:44,755 --> 01:01:47,425
<font color=#FFFF00>But everything seems to be...</font>

961
01:01:50,325 --> 01:01:52,155
<font color=#FFFF00>so confusing right now.</font>

962
01:01:55,125 --> 01:01:56,625
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know what the truth is,</font>

963
01:01:58,885 --> 01:02:01,055
<font color=#FFFF00>or whether I should know the truth or not.</font>

964
01:02:03,285 --> 01:02:04,385
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know...</font>

965
01:02:06,655 --> 01:02:08,785
<font color=#FFFF00>why this is happening to me.</font>

966
01:02:11,625 --> 01:02:12,825
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know any of that.</font>

967
01:02:17,855 --> 01:02:19,185
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han.</font>

968
01:02:24,225 --> 01:02:25,885
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know what I should do.</font>

969
01:02:27,285 --> 01:02:29,525
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm so confused.</font>

970
01:02:34,055 --> 01:02:36,155
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know where things went wrong,</font>

971
01:02:37,225 --> 01:02:38,285
<font color=#FFFF00>and...</font>

972
01:02:40,085 --> 01:02:42,325
<font color=#FFFF00>what happens to the things I've believed until now.</font>

973
01:02:45,385 --> 01:02:46,585
<font color=#FFFF00>I feel like dying.</font>

974
01:02:49,685 --> 01:02:50,855
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han.</font>

975
01:02:53,085 --> 01:02:54,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't do this.</font>

976
01:02:54,755 --> 01:02:57,225
<font color=#FFFF00>I know you're a strong person.</font>

977
01:02:58,485 --> 01:02:59,725
<font color=#FFFF00>Please calm down.</font>

978
01:03:12,755 --> 01:03:14,225
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't cry.</font>

979
01:03:14,755 --> 01:03:16,925
<font color=#FFFF00>You're making me want to cry, too.</font>

980
01:04:02,455 --> 01:04:03,985
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing?</font>

981
01:04:04,555 --> 01:04:05,825
<font color=#FFFF00>Seon Mi is doing a good job.</font>

982
01:04:06,485 --> 01:04:08,255
<font color=#FFFF00>They're going to eat and drink all night.</font>

983
01:04:08,325 --> 01:04:10,025
<font color=#FFFF00>People just love free stuff.</font>

984
01:04:11,555 --> 01:04:14,855
<font color=#FFFF00>- This is great. - Can I have some more beer?</font>

985
01:04:15,325 --> 01:04:18,355
<font color=#FFFF00>What did you tell them the free food was for?</font>

986
01:04:18,355 --> 01:04:20,525
<font color=#FFFF00>I told them today is the day my brother died.</font>

987
01:04:20,725 --> 01:04:22,885
<font color=#FFFF00>I told them I was feeding chicken to people...</font>

988
01:04:22,955 --> 01:04:24,655
<font color=#FFFF00>in my dead brother's age to honor him.</font>

989
01:04:24,655 --> 01:04:25,655
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, Seong Hoon!</font>

990
01:04:26,025 --> 01:04:27,655
<font color=#FFFF00>This is all your fault!</font>

991
01:04:27,655 --> 01:04:29,525
<font color=#FFFF00>You handed over the documents!</font>

992
01:04:29,525 --> 01:04:31,055
<font color=#FFFF00>Lower your voice, you brat.</font>

993
01:04:31,685 --> 01:04:33,125
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing?</font>

994
01:04:33,485 --> 01:04:34,755
<font color=#FFFF00>We've got to go home.</font>

995
01:04:36,055 --> 01:04:38,285
<font color=#FFFF00>Be quiet and duck down.</font>

996
01:04:56,685 --> 01:04:57,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, I'm exhausted.</font>

997
01:04:58,085 --> 01:05:00,855
<font color=#FFFF00>Are we safe now, Seong Hoon?</font>

998
01:05:02,355 --> 01:05:04,125
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go home.</font>

999
01:05:04,425 --> 01:05:05,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, Hee Sook.</font>

1000
01:05:05,985 --> 01:05:07,085
<font color=#FFFF00>Well done.</font>

1001
01:05:07,425 --> 01:05:08,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Let's go in.</font>

1002
01:05:12,585 --> 01:05:13,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, I'm so tired.</font>

1003
01:05:13,885 --> 01:05:15,785
<font color=#FFFF00>- It's Han Seong Sik. - That's Han Seong Sik!</font>

1004
01:05:16,455 --> 01:05:18,225
<font color=#FFFF00>- Oh my goodness. - Wait!</font>

1005
01:05:18,225 --> 01:05:19,755
<font color=#FFFF00>- Stop! - What are you doing?</font>

1006
01:05:19,755 --> 01:05:21,355
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it true that you illegally counselled...</font>

1007
01:05:21,355 --> 01:05:23,585
<font color=#FFFF00>Seonghan Group to be nominated to Minjeong Party?</font>

1008
01:05:23,585 --> 01:05:24,885
<font color=#FFFF00>No, it's not.</font>

1009
01:05:24,885 --> 01:05:26,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you really play a role as a broker...</font>

1010
01:05:26,755 --> 01:05:28,355
<font color=#FFFF00>for Minjeong Party and Seonghan Group?</font>

1011
01:05:28,355 --> 01:05:30,725
<font color=#FFFF00>No, he didn't. Don't do this.</font>

1012
01:05:30,725 --> 01:05:32,725
<font color=#FFFF00>- He doesn't know anything. - Come, Seong Sik.</font>

1013
01:05:32,825 --> 01:05:34,555
<font color=#FFFF00>- Stop it already. - Are you having an affair...</font>

1014
01:05:34,555 --> 01:05:36,025
<font color=#FFFF00>with Jang Yoo Ra, the news anchor?</font>

1015
01:05:39,185 --> 01:05:42,425
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it true that you bribed an official for Jang Yoo Ra?</font>

1016
01:05:42,485 --> 01:05:45,355
<font color=#FFFF00>How is she related to your illegal counselling?</font>

1017
01:05:46,055 --> 01:05:47,885
<font color=#FFFF00>What are they talking about?</font>

1018
01:05:48,025 --> 01:05:50,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Hoon. I don't know anything about this.</font>

1019
01:05:50,125 --> 01:05:52,225
<font color=#FFFF00>I really don't know.</font>

1020
01:05:53,125 --> 01:05:54,155
<font color=#FFFF00>You are...</font>

1021
01:05:56,225 --> 01:05:57,385
<font color=#FFFF00>having an affair with her?</font>

1022
01:05:57,555 --> 01:05:59,325
<font color=#FFFF00>What are they talking about?</font>

